<title>UK: U.S. Hilfiger sues UK's Littlewoods.</title>
<headline>U.S. Hilfiger sues UK's Littlewoods.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-04-04</dateline>
<text>
<p>U.S. designer Tommy Hilfiger Corporation said on Friday it was seeking compensation and damages in a writ filed in March in London against Littlewoods Warehouses Ltd, a unit of Britain's largest private retail and leisure group Littlewoods.</p>
<p>&quot;The company alleges that Littlewoods has been selling merchandise that infringes various Tommy Hilfiger trademarks,&quot; Hilfiger, a leading U.S. fashion house which plans to open its first store in London in autumn, said in a statement.</p>
